{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C3019 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C3019 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"content":"Compiler Error C3019","pos":[597,617]},{"content":"increment in OpenMP 'for' statement has improper form","pos":[618,671]},{"pos":[678,797],"content":"The increment part of an OpenMP <ph id=\"ph1\">`for`</ph> loop must use the index variable both on the left and right side of the operator.","source":"The increment part of an OpenMP `for` loop must use the index variable both on the left and right side of the operator."},{"content":"The following sample generates C3019:","pos":[804,841]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C3019 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-cpp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"error-reference\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C3019\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C3019\"\nms.assetid: 31a6d9b6-d29f-4499-9ad8-48dd751e87c7\ncaps.latest.revision: 7\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C3019\nincrement in OpenMP 'for' statement has improper form  \n  \n The increment part of an OpenMP `for` loop must use the index variable both on the left and right side of the operator.  \n  \n The following sample generates C3019:  \n  \n```  \n// C3019.cpp  \n// compile with: /openmp  \nint main()  \n{  \n   int i = 0, j = 1, n = 3;  \n  \n   #pragma omp parallel  \n   {  \n      #pragma omp for  \n      for (i = 0; i < 10; i = j + n)   // C3019  \n      // Try the following line instead:  \n      // for (i = 0; i < 10; i++)  \n         j *= 2;  \n   }  \n}  \n```"}